boss.
   _Carl Angelo ``Toughy'' DeLuna, reputed Kansas City family
underboss.
   _Carl ``Corky'' Civella, reputed Kansas City family capo.
   
   Not in prison:
   _Anthony Thomas ``Tony Ripe'' Civella, Kansas City, Mo., reputed
Kansas City family capo.
   _Nicholas ``Nicky Glasses'' Marangello, reputed Bonanno
underboss, Bronx, N.Y.
   _John ``Peanuts'' Tronolone, Miami Beach, Fla., reputed
high-ranking member of Cleveland crime family, alleged Genovese
associate, acquitted with Salerno and Rockman of union election
tampering.
