<FILEID>AP-NR-06-29-88 2257EDT</FILEID>
<1ST_LINE>u i AM-HongKong-Gold     06-29 0030</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>AM-Hong Kong-Gold,0028</2ND_LINE>
<HEAD>Gold Down</HEAD>
<DATELINE>HONG KONG (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Gold dropped $1.77 ounce on the Kong Kong
