<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The stock market turned downward today after an
early advance faded.
   The Dow Jones average of 30 industrials, up about 7 points in
the early going, was down 10.14 at 2,120.73 by noontime on Wall
Street.
   Losers outnumbered gainers by about 4 to 3 in the overall tally
of New York Stock Exchange-listed issues, with 529 up, 714 down and
541 unchanged.
